## ğŸ”§ Configuration

### Supported News Sources

- **BBC News** (`https://www.bbc.com/`)
- **Dawn** (`https://www.dawn.com/`)
- **Al Jazeera** (`https://www.aljazeera.com/`)
- **Reuters, CNN** (via web scraping)

